{"tid":2354101,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"3 月發佈 ? Apple 新款 14\" 16\" Macbook 或升級至 12 / 16 核心自研處理器 $AAPL","createTime":"2021-01-05T08:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T11:24:47.000Z","uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b7cb7fec2251bcb905976e892e5a7b05c8ad3518","tid":2354101,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:18:05.000Z","msg":"2020 年尾，Apple 推出搭載自研 M1 八核心處理器的 Mac 產品，並成功獲得大量支持。由於 Apple 已打算在兩年內將 Mac 產品線退出 Intel 處理器，所以不難猜測更多 M 系列晶片正在準備當中。<br />\n<br />\n根據最新的爆料指，新款 Mac 產品預定於 3 月發佈，將搭載 12 核心 Apple Silicon 晶片。至於關於這款 Mac 規格，在爆料中並無給出細節，但若以知名分析師郭明錤的說法，可能會是 14.1&Prime; 與 16&Prime; MacBook Pro。同時有猜測認為，14&Prime;  或搭載 12 核心處理器、16&Prime; 則升級至 16 核心處理器。不同於 x86 架構，ARM 晶片對於增加核心更容易，同時功耗亦能壓得住。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，12 核、16 核的新處理器可能不會以 M2 命名，因早前有消息指，M2 將選擇於 iMac 上首發，由於是 AIO PC，CPU、GPU 單元的規模更加可觀。考量到目前 8 核心 M1 晶片的優秀表現，特別是在 macOS 下，即將到來的 12 核心、16 核心晶片更讓人值得期待。<br />\n$AAPL"},{"pid":"112a2696e07acc9e9240ca91ad1db473a3c3fe1c","tid":2354101,"uid":180401,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"無可能禁快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都想"},{"pid":"0adc8dc8714839741b97fbc11017e4dbc01dde41","tid":2354101,"uid":195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"14&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7346b2388fab798d8aff9ef93c58755ad33844b","tid":2354101,"uid":2590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e930c8499a9469915c8fe1c76b2546f7467ccdde","tid":2354101,"uid":109923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"連登仔：Apple唧牙膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /